headline: Trimble Extends Midwest Reach With West Side Tractor Partnership And Outlook
summary: Trimble (NasdaqGS:TRMB) named West Side Tractor Sales Co. a new Trimble Technology Outlet and authorized reseller. The partnership expands access to Trimble grade control and positioning systems for John Deere equipment users in northern Illinois, Indiana, and select Michigan counties. West Side Tractor Sales Co. will provide sales, installation, training, and support for Trimble construction technology solutions.
